HEADWORD: Fortnightly
<hw>Fort"night`ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Occurring or
appearing once in a fortnight; <as>as, a <ex>fortnightly</ex> meeting of
a club; a <ex>fortnightly</ex> magazine, or other
publication.</as></def> -- <def2><pos>adv.</pos> <def>Once in a
fortnight; at intervals of a fortnight.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

